<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美罗城美术馆里挤满了人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都为能看到新画感到非常兴奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些画真美。”一个女人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的丈夫点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，它们非常……啊！发生什么事了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>浓雾渐渐弥漫了整个房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我什么都看不到了！”一个声音喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44949</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>浓雾消散时，一个女人吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！那些画不见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快看我！”杰克喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他以最快的速度跑过特勒尔家的后院。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他猛地一跳——扑通！——落在了一堆叶子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>叶子飞得到处都是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！”罗西大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“轮到我了！”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都拿起耙子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们开始用耙子重新把树叶堆成一堆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快轮到玛拉跳了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走到后院的尽头，然后跑向树叶堆并往上一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇喔！”玛拉喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太有意思了。”特勒尔拿起耙子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109683</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“秋天是我最喜欢的季节。我喜欢凉爽的天气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我喜欢在树叶堆里玩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我最喜欢的季节是冬天。”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢在雪里玩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我期待着下雪天赶快到来。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望现在就下雪！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在天气还太暖和。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得最近几个月都不会下雪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对。”杰克叹了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家又用耙子把树叶堆成了一堆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这次轮到罗西跳了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”罗西大喊着跳进了树叶堆里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家再次把树叶堆成一堆的时候，特勒尔想到了一个主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们应该请求火箭女孩儿去让老天下雪！”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个想法太可笑了。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿无法控制天气。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是她有超能力！”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185541</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没等罗西回答，她的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘不好了。’她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看了朋友们一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，朋友们。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我想起来我告诉过妈妈中午回家吃饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我待会儿再回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西一走到特勒尔家门前就马上接通了电话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长。”她说，“发生什么事了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们有麻烦了，火箭女孩儿。”布洛姆市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生了一起盗窃案。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有美罗城美术馆里的新画都被偷了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，市长。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿出发了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>